      <p>The overall risk assessment is <strong class="text-white">HIGH</strong>. Extended valuations combined with building macro pressures — rate hike pricing, oil supply shock, physical bottlenecks — create the conditions for a significant correction within the broader secular AI trend.</p>

      <p>The recommended positioning is clear:</p>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-300 ml-4">
